data.description: SELLER OFFERING 10K IN CLOSING COSTS FOR BUYER! Welcome to your dream home in sought after South Forsyth!  Offering an open floor concept this home creates a seamless flow throughout, perfect for entertaining and everyday living.   As you enter, you'll be greeted by vaulted ceilings and an impressive two-story great room that is flooded with natural light from the abundance of windows. MASTER ON MAIN with updated bathroom. Upstairs, you'll find two additional bedrooms and an oversized bonus room, providing ample space for a growing family or guests. The full basement features a large bedroom with an updated bathroom, a home theater for movie nights, and a spacious flex space that can be used as a workout room or game room. And TONS of natural lighting! Additional man cave room and a storage space/workshop area with an insulated garage door connected to the side of the home making it easy to store your lawn mower! Great sized lot with fenced-in backyard. Newly renovated back deck and large patio underneath are perfect for outdoor entertaining. Neighborhood amenities include courtesy dock on Lake Lanier, a covered picnic pavilion, swim and tennis facilities, a playground, and a clubhouse, all adjacent to the beautiful Mary Alice Park.Located just minutes away from the Cumming City Center, Bald Ridge & Habersham Marinas, Northside Hospital, and award-winning schools.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this extraordinary home yours!
